metadata.name: loneliness is removed by friends
metadata.description: Chapter One: The Child Who Was Always Left Alone in the library He often fell asleep with piles of books in loneliness. Waking up early on a rainy day. He saw the characters in the book looking at him with friendly expressions. and everyone invites each other to play until they forget the time But the little boy didn't forget to draw a picture to keep as a memory. But before it was finished, there was a small voice shouting, "Let's go play outside." The image paralleled 3500x4000 px.
